               <p>JOHN GUNTER. I live in <placeName id="t18220522-116-crimeloc616">Paradise-walk, Chelsea</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18220522-116-crimeloc616" type="placeName" value="Paradise-walk, Chelsea"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18220522-116-crimeloc616" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220522-116-off614 t18220522-116-crimeloc616"></join>. The prisoner lived two doors off. On the 22d of April, I went out at two o'clock and returned at seven, the watch was gone from my bed-room; I had left the back door open. The prisoner was taken on the 29th, and said he took it.</p>
               <p>
            
